    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Gift Recommendations, Part 3\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to get gift recommendations for your friend.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Copy and paste** the following prompt or use your customized prompt from the previous level:\r\n\r\n>Give me 3 gift ideas under $30 for a 15-year-old girl who likes watercolor paintings. Her favorite birthday gift last year was a purple Polaroid camera. Justify your answer based on her decorating style in this picture of her room.\r\n2. Choose one of the pre-loaded images from the images folder to represent the gift recipient’s room decoration style.\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n4. Read **AI Chat's response**.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n::: details [**How do I upload an image?**]\r\n- Click the tab labeled **Images** on the top left.\r\n- Then browse the existing images.\r\n- When you have an image to upload, click to select it and then click Upload.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n",
